attributes.action: save Dudleys, Holly Hall walk in centre from closure
attributes.additional_details:
THIS IS AN OUT OF HOURS WALK IN CENTRE WHICH IS SET FOR CLOSURE. BAD IDEA! VERY MUCH NEEDED IN THE AREA, TO KEEP THE PRESSURE OFF OTHER RESOURCES (A&E).
PLEASE KEEP THIS SERVICE OPEN, AS THERE WOULD NOT BE ANOTHER OPTION AVAILABLE FOR SICK PEOPLE, NOT REQUIRING ACCIDENT & EMERGENCY DEPARTMENT
